Max Steel (2013) - Season 1 - Episodes 25 and 26 (WEB-DL - 720p)
----------------------------------------------------------------

A high-octane, action-packed superhero series about the epic adventures of
earthbound teenager Maxwell McGrath and his out-of-this-world friend Steel.
On his sixteenth birthday, Maxwell learns that he has the ability to generate
TURBO ENERGY, the most powerful energy in the universe. While the energy gives
Max incredible powers, he can't always control it. Fortunately he meets Steel,
an intergalactic alien war machine, powered by Turbo Energy - which enables Max
to take charge of his own power. Together Max and Steel defend the planet from
all manner of mayhem, monsters and extraterrestrial invasion as the world's
greatest new superhero, Max Steel!

Produced by Nerd Corps Entertainment and Mattel Studios.
